      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi everyone! I\u2019m so excited to share this absolute gem with you. If you\u2019re looking for a car that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, this is the one! It\u2019s in truly pristine, flawless condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one and it\u2019s been kept tucked away in the garage. Not a single scratch or smudge to be found, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon. Come take a look and fall in love!",
