    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presented is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in flawless condition. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring a high-pressure dual-VANOS system and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response and a linear power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline. This example boasts a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement, and the suspension utilizes a refreshed MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup for optimal kinematics. The coachwork is pristine, exhibiting factory panel tolerances and a deep, swirl-free finish. Mechanically sound with fully documented valve adjustments and rod bearing services, this is a superlative specimen for the performance enthusiast seeking a turnkey collector car.",
      "price": 46500.0,
